\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {18.1}{\ignorespaces Architecture of the SlyOS shared inference layer. A single optimized foundation model serves all applications; each app provides only an isolated RAG context (10--100\,MB) that is dynamically swapped in milliseconds. The intelligent router determines when to serve on-device versus escalating to cloud. This eliminates redundant model storage and RAM competition across applications.\relax }}{132}{figure.caption.47}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:shared_daemon}{{18.1}{132}{Architecture of the SlyOS shared inference layer. A single optimized foundation model serves all applications; each app provides only an isolated RAG context (10--100\,MB) that is dynamically swapped in milliseconds. The intelligent router determines when to serve on-device versus escalating to cloud. This eliminates redundant model storage and RAM competition across applications.\relax }{figure.caption.47}{}}
